This is a (incomplete) sample app written as a Webiva module that includes a custom route at
/things for displaying the AppSample::ThingsController RESTful controller.

To use this in a site, install the module as app_sample in vendor/modules/
Activate the module inside of Webiva, 
then add a page at /things into the site tree and a "Module App" paragraph where you would like
the app to show up.

